# Bulk Mg21Zn25 single point energy

units metal
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p

read_data bulk_structure/mg21zn25_relaxed.data

pair_style meam
pair_coeff * * library.meam Mg Zn ZnMg.meam Zn Mg

fix 1 all box/relax iso 0.0 vmax 0.001
minimize 1.0e-8 1.0e-10 10000 100000
unfix 1

thermo 1
thermo_style custom step pe etotal press vol

run 0
